<section class="space-time" id="why-tar">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="sticky-intro" data-animate>
      <div class="badge">Architecture</div>
      <h2 class="title">Built for <br/><span class="accent">Space-Time Scale</span></h2>
      <p class="description">
        Traditional systems are built for the web. <br/>
        <strong>TAR is built for the physical world.</strong>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="scale-grid">
      <div class="scale-item" data-animate>
        <div class="scale-visual">
          <div class="coord-system">
            <div class="axis x"></div>
            <div class="axis y"></div>
            <div class="axis z"></div>
            <div class="point p1"></div>
            <div class="point p2"></div>
            <div class="point p3"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="scale-info">
          <span class="num">01</span>
          <h3>The Dimension of Space</h3>
          <p>Every asset, rider, and event is assigned a precise coordinate. We don't just "list" items; we map their existence in a global H3-indexed grid.</p>
          <ul class="stats">
            <li>Precision: 1mÂ²</li>
            <li>Indexing: H3-Level 15</li>
            <li>Native Geo-Sharding</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="scale-item reverse" data-animate>
        <div class="scale-visual">
          <div class="time-stream">
            <div class="wave"></div>
            <div class="wave"></div>
            <div class="wave"></div>
            <div class="playhead"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="scale-info">
          <span class="num">02</span>
          <h3>The Dimension of Time</h3>
          <p>Time isn't just a timestamp in TAR. It's a traversable stream. Trace records every micro-event, allowing AI agents to replay history and predict future spikes.</p>
          <ul class="stats">
            <li>Throughput: 1.2M events/s</li>
            <li>Resolution: Nanoseconds</li>
            <li>Zero-loss Persistence</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="scale-item" data-animate>
        <div class="scale-visual">
          <div class="ai-nervous-system">
            <div class="core"></div>
            <div class="connection"></div>
            <div class="connection"></div>
            <div class="connection"></div>
            <div class="node-small"></div>
            <div class="node-small"></div>
            <div class="node-small"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="scale-info">
          <span class="num">03</span>
          <h3>The Intelligence Layer</h3>
          <p>Where Space and Time meet, Agents are born. Autonomous intelligence that lives at the edge, deciding and acting without human dashboards.</p>
          <ul class="stats">
            <li>Local-first Inference</li>
            <li>Decentralized Logic</li>
            <li>Autonomous Recovery</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .space-time {
    background: #000000;
    color: #ffffff;
    padding: 160px 0;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 40px;
  }

  .sticky-intro {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 120px;
  }

  .badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 6px 14px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .title {
    font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 10vw, 6.5rem);
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .title .accent {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .description {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .description strong {
    color: #ffffff;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* Grid System */
  .scale-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 160px;
  }

  .scale-item {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .scale-item.reverse {
    direction: rtl;
  }

  .scale-item.reverse .scale-info {
    direction: ltr;
  }

  .scale-visual {
    position: relative;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);
    border-radius: 40px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
  }

  .num {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 4rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    opacity: 0.3;
    display: block;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .scale-info h3 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .scale-info p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .stats {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .stats li {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: #ffffff;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
  }

  /* Visual Elements */
  .coord-system {
    position: relative;
    width: 200px;
    height: 200px;
  }

  .axis {
    position: absolute;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .axis.x { width: 100%; height: 1px; top: 50%; left: 0; }
  .axis.y { width: 1px; height: 100%; left: 50%; top: 0; }
  .axis.z { width: 140%; height: 1px; top: 50%; left: -20%; transform: rotate(45deg); }

  .point {
    position: absolute;
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: 50%;
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--color-accent);
    animation: drift 6s infinite alternate ease-in-out;
  }

  .p2 { top: 20%; left: 30%; animation-delay: -1s; }
  .p3 { bottom: 25%; right: 20%; animation-delay: -3s; }

  @keyframes drift {
    from { transform: translate(0, 0); }
    to { transform: translate(20px, -20px); }
  }

  .time-stream {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 0 40px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .wave {
    height: 60px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    border-radius: 30px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.05), transparent);
    animation: slide 3s infinite linear;
  }

  @keyframes slide {
    from { background-position: -200% 0; }
    to { background-position: 200% 0; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .scale-item, .scale-item.reverse {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 48px;
      direction: ltr;
    }
    .scale-visual {
      aspect-ratio: 16/9;
    }
    .title {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
